-family": "\\"Lato\\", sans-serif"}, "pageId": "9461c09e-a437-49b0-9a51-d040d7edf431", "childrens": [], "childrenIds": [], "application_id": "838669d8-92d2-4342-baba-5f32a40eef42", "component_type": "rich-text"}, {"name": "text_label_3184_rnst", "uuid": "2011342c-5804-4cba-ba60-909dcf6c938e", "input": {"value": {"type": "value", "value": "Button"}}, "style": {"fontSize": "30px", "margin-top": "10px", "font-family": "\\"Mulish\\", sans-serif"}, "pageId": "9461c09e-a437-49b0-9a51-d040d7edf431", "childrens": [], "childrenIds": [], "application_id": "838669d8-92d2-4342-baba-5f32a40eef42", "component_type": "text_label"}, {"name": "rich-text_700", "uuid": "f334cdb8-64a8-4067-8d11-153d297381a8", "input": {"value": {"type": "string", "value": "<h2 class=\\"anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_LWe7\\" id=\\"when-to-use\\" style=\\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(28, 30, 33); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; line-height: 1.25; margin: 40px 0px 20px; font-size: 32px; scroll-margin-top: 68px; --ifm-h2-font-size: 2rem;\\">When To Use<a href=\\"https://hybridui.github.io/docs/docs/components/buttons#when-to-use\\" class=\\"hash-link\\" aria-label=\\"Direct link to When To Use\\" title=\\"Direct link to When To Use\\" style=\\"box-sizing: border-box; transition: opacity 0.2s; color: rgb(46, 133, 85); text-decoration-line: none; text-decoration-style: solid; text-decoration-color: rgb(46, 133, 85); opacity: 0; padding-left: 0.5rem; user-select: none;\\">ÃƒÆ’Ã†â€™Ãƒâ€ Ã¢â‚¬â„¢ÃƒÆ’Ã¢â‚¬Â ÃƒÂ¢Ã¢â€šÂ¬Ã¢â€žÂ¢ÃƒÆ’Ã†â€™ÃƒÂ¢Ã¢â€šÂ¬Ã‚Â ÃƒÆ’Ã‚Â¢ÃƒÂ¢Ã¢â‚¬Å¡Ã‚Â¬ÃƒÂ¢Ã¢â‚¬Å¾Ã‚Â¢ÃƒÆ’Ã†â€™Ãƒâ€ Ã¢â‚¬â„¢ÃƒÆ’Ã‚Â¢ÃƒÂ¢Ã¢â‚¬Å¡Ã‚Â¬Ãƒâ€¦Ã‚Â¡ÃƒÆ’Ã†â€™ÃƒÂ¢Ã¢â€šÂ¬Ã…Â¡ÃƒÆ’Ã¢â‚¬Å¡Ãƒâ€šÃ‚Â¢ÃƒÆ’Ã†â€™Ãƒâ€ Ã¢â‚¬â„¢ÃƒÆ’Ã¢â‚¬Â ÃƒÂ¢Ã¢â€šÂ¬Ã¢â€žÂ¢ÃƒÆ’Ã†â€™ÃƒÂ¢Ã¢â€šÂ¬Ã…Â¡ÃƒÆ’Ã¢â‚¬Å¡Ãƒâ€šÃ‚Â¢ÃƒÆ’Ã†â€™Ãƒâ€ Ã¢â‚¬â„¢ÃƒÆ’Ã¢â‚¬Å¡Ãƒâ€šÃ‚Â¢ÃƒÆ’Ã†â€™Ãƒâ€šÃ‚Â¢ÃƒÆ’Ã‚Â¢ÃƒÂ¢Ã¢â‚¬Å¡Ã‚Â¬Ãƒâ€¦Ã‚Â¡ÃƒÆ’Ã¢â‚¬Å¡Ãƒâ€šÃ‚Â¬ÃƒÆ’Ã†â€™ÃƒÂ¢Ã¢â€šÂ¬Ã‚Â¦ÃƒÆ’Ã¢â‚¬Å¡Ãƒâ€šÃ‚Â¡ÃƒÆ’Ã†â€™Ãƒâ€ Ã¢â‚¬â„¢ÃƒÆ’Ã‚Â¢ÃƒÂ¢Ã¢â‚¬Å¡Ã‚Â¬Ãƒâ€¦Ã‚Â¡ÃƒÆ’Ã†â€™ÃƒÂ¢Ã¢â€šÂ¬Ã…Â¡ÃƒÆ’Ã¢â‚¬Å¡Ãƒâ€šÃ‚Â¬ÃƒÆ’Ã†â€™Ãƒâ€ Ã¢â‚¬â„¢ÃƒÆ’Ã¢â‚¬Â ÃƒÂ¢Ã¢â€šÂ¬Ã¢â€žÂ¢ÃƒÆ’Ã†â€™ÃƒÂ¢Ã¢â€šÂ¬Ã…Â¡ÃƒÆ’Ã¢â‚¬Å¡Ãƒâ€šÃ‚Â¢ÃƒÆ’Ã†â€™Ãƒâ€ Ã¢â‚¬â„¢ÃƒÆ’Ã¢â‚¬Å¡Ãƒâ€šÃ‚Â¢ÃƒÆ’Ã†â€™Ãƒâ€šÃ‚Â¢ÃƒÆ’Ã‚Â¢ÃƒÂ¢Ã¢â€šÂ¬Ã…Â¡Ãƒâ€šÃ‚Â¬ÃƒÆ’Ã¢â‚¬Â¦Ãƒâ€šÃ‚Â¡ÃƒÆ’Ã†â€™ÃƒÂ¢Ã¢â€šÂ¬Ã…Â¡ÃƒÆ’Ã¢â‚¬Å¡Ãƒâ€šÃ‚Â¬ÃƒÆ’Ã†â€™Ãƒâ€ Ã¢â‚¬â„¢ÃƒÆ’Ã‚Â¢ÃƒÂ¢Ã¢â‚¬Å¡Ã‚Â¬Ãƒâ€¦Ã‚Â¡ÃƒÆ’Ã†â€™ÃƒÂ¢Ã¢â€šÂ¬Ã…Â¡ÃƒÆ’Ã¢â‚¬Å¡Ãƒâ€šÃ‚Â¹</a></h2><p style=\\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; color: rgb(28, 30, 33); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-size: 16px;\\">Buttons in Hybrid Design are used to perform one or more operations. When clicked, a button triggers the corresponding business logic. In Hybrid Design, we offer five types of buttons:</p><ul class=\\"\\" style=\\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding-left: 32px; color: rgb(28, 30, 33); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-size: 16px;\\"><li style=\\"box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word;\\">Primary button: This button indicates the main action and there should only be one primary button in each section.</li><li style=\\"box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 4px;\\">Default button: This button represents a series of actions without priority.</li><li style=\\"box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 4px;\\">Dashed button: This button is commonly used for adding an action.</li><li style=\\"box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 4px;\\">Text button: This button is used for the most secondary action.</li><li style=\\"box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 4px;\\">Link button: This button is used for external links.</li></ul><p style=\\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; color: rgb(28, 30, 33); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-size: 16px;\\">Additionally, we have four other properties that can be applied to any type of button:</p><ul class=\\"\\" style=\\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding-left: 32px; color: rgb(28, 30, 33); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-size: 16px;\\"><li style=\\"box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word;\\"><code style=\\"box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: middle; background-color: rgb(246, 247, 248); border: 0.1rem solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); border-radius: 6.4px; font-family: SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 15.2px; padding: 1.6px;\\">danger</code>: This property is used for actions that involve risk, such as deletion or authorization.</li><li style=\\"box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 4px;\\"><code style=\\"box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: middle; background-color: rgb(246, 247, 248); border: 0.1rem solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); border-radius: 6.4px; font-family: SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 15.2px; padding: 1.6px;\\">disabled</code>: This property indicates when actions are not available.</li><li style=\\"box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 4px;\\"><code style=\\"box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: middle; background-color: rgb(246, 247, 248); border: 0.1rem solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); border-radius: 6.4px; font-family: SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 15.2px; padding: 1.6px;\\">loading</code>: This property adds a loading spinner to the button, preventing multiple submits.</li></ul><p style=\\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; color: rgb(28, 30, 33); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-size: 16px;\\">In HybridUI, the available button types are primary, default, dashed, text, and link.</p>"}}, "pageId": "9461c09e-a437-49b0-9a51-d040d7edf431", "childrens": [], "childrenIds": [], "application_id": "838669d8-92d2-4342-baba-5f32a40eef42", "component_type": "rich-text"}, {"name": "button-demo-block", "uuid": "13ad228c-d0c6-4362-b072-87de7c43ff26", "pageId": "9461c09e-a437-49b0-9a51-d040d7edf431", "childrens": [{"name": "button_input_1901_r5tx", "uuid": "d99fdc90-d1ea-44bd-b578-159469287e4a", "input": {"label": {"type": "value", "value": "Primary button"}}, "style": {"type": "primary"}, "pageId": "9461c09e-a437-49b0-9a51-d040d7edf431", "childrens": [], "childrenIds": [], "application_id": "838669d8-92d2-4342-baba-5f32a40eef42", "component_type": "button_input"}, {"name": "button_input_